---
title: Glazed Chicken with Green Beans and Coconut Rice
description: Rice is the ultimate side dish. It’s hearty, versatile, and beloved by even the pickiest of eaters. In this recipe, we take this classic side up a notch by infusing it with rich, slightly sweet coconut milk. It pairs with juicy chicken and crispy green beans for an all-around awesome dinner.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/teriyaki-chicken-with-coconut-ri-ed7c07df.jpg
